      "message": "We can turn it into a computed value, but computed value will only be cached when accessed by an observer.\nthis._allTests however will be used during actions (non-observer), so using @observable is better than @computed.\n\nAn alternative is to use keepAlive with @computed, but mobx doc says that could cause memory leak.\nhttps://mobx.js.org/refguide/computed-decorator.html",
